From c7dc5aeaa3e22f9eebcf7835932c9659fb636b3e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Francesco Pham <francesco.pham1@h-partners.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Apr 2026 19:16:08 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] hybris: create /storage/cloud/<userId>/files for
 MediaLibrary

MediaLibrary's ROOT_MEDIA_DIR check requires /storage/cloud/<userId>/files
to exist; without it the service self-kills and the normal-app file picker
(VLC "Open File" etc.) returns empty. Adding the entry makes storage_daemon
create the directory at user start.

See phase12_sharefs_user_files.md (Phase 12.1, 2026-04-16).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Change-Id: Ie3d0540982793795569022f72c40a39d54acf422
---
 services/storage_daemon/storage_user_path.json | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/services/storage_daemon/storage_user_path.json b/services/storage_daemon/storage_user_path.json
index 023e57ba..e6087a05 100644
--- a/services/storage_daemon/storage_user_path.json
+++ b/services/storage_daemon/storage_user_path.json
@@ -790,6 +790,12 @@
             "uid": 1008,
             "gid": 1008
         },
+        {
+            "path": "/storage/cloud/<userId>/files",
+            "mode": "0711",
+            "uid": 1008,
+            "gid": 1008
+        },
         {
             "path": "/mnt/share/",
             "mode": "0711",
-- 
